1
00:00:02,011 --> 00:00:04,359
Some devotees told Guru Maharaj, 
once they’ve said,

2
00:00:04,359 --> 00:00:06,297
“After all these years,

3
00:00:06,487 --> 00:00:09,167
you know, taking the Holy Name, 
reading Srimad-Bhagavatam, etc ...”

4
00:00:09,167 --> 00:00:15,083
he said, “I’m not ... My enthusiasm,

5
00:00:15,083 --> 00:00:18,873
hankering for reading the Bhagavatam, 
it’s gone down”,

6
00:00:18,873 --> 00:00:20,432
this person said.

7
00:00:20,492 --> 00:00:23,622
[Hunger is Symptom of Health]

8
00:00:23,722 --> 00:00:26,878
And Guru Maharaj have said, 
“Well, then stop reading the Bhagavatam”.

9
00:00:26,878 --> 00:00:29,232
He said, “No, I don’t want to do that!”

10
00:00:29,232 --> 00:00:33,820
And Guru Maharaj have said, 
“Oh, then you do have some appreciation.

11
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:39,359
Just not as great 
as you might imagine or hope for.”

12
00:00:39,539 --> 00:00:45,109
But in that Bhagavatam 
we also hear about hunger.

13
00:00:45,230 --> 00:00:49,163
And Guru Maharaj’s saying, 
“Hunger is symptomatic of health.”

14
00:00:49,163 --> 00:00:53,203
dharmaḥ svanuṣṭhitaḥ puṁsāṁ
viṣvaksena-kathāsu yaḥ

15
00:00:53,203 --> 00:00:57,043
notpādayed yadi ratiṁ
śrama eva hi kevalam 
[SB: 1.2.8]

16
00:00:57,353 --> 00:01:03,202
A way to measure whether or not 
we’re properly adjusted

17
00:01:03,202 --> 00:01:05,064
[is] whatever it is 
you’re doing,

18
00:01:05,064 --> 00:01:07,974
if the end result 
is increased attraction

19
00:01:07,974 --> 00:01:10,434
for hearing, chanting, 
remembering, serving,

20
00:01:10,434 --> 00:01:12,368
then you’re going 
in a right direction.

21
00:01:12,368 --> 00:01:15,634
If whatever you’re doing 
it’s going in the opposite direction,

22
00:01:15,634 --> 00:01:19,091
you need ... 
It’s time for readjustment.

23
00:01:19,091 --> 00:01:23,622
kāmasya nendriya-prītir 
lābho jīveta yāvatā

24
00:01:23,622 --> 00:01:28,922
jīvasya tattva-jijñāsā 
nārtho yaś ceha karmabhiḥ 
[SB: 1.2.10]

25
00:01:29,062 --> 00:01:30,572
Same thing.

26
00:01:30,682 --> 00:01:36,992
Life should be structured 
in such a way as to

27
00:01:37,862 --> 00:01:42,333
minimise one’s involvement 
with the mundane

28
00:01:42,333 --> 00:01:47,073
or arrange the mundane 
in such a way that it’s

29
00:01:47,473 --> 00:01:53,852
a launching pad or catalyst 
for your spiritual culture.

30
00:01:53,862 --> 00:01:57,682
Structure your life, 
arrange things in a such a way

31
00:01:57,682 --> 00:02:01,862
as you can engage 
in a maximum amount of spiritual culture.

